  <brief_title>Enrichment &amp; Purging of Stem Cells in Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Enrichment and Purging of Stem Cells in the Treatment of Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma</official_title>
